                <b:Paragraph>
                    <b>Transition animations not supported in Internet Explorer 8 &amp;
                        9
                    </b>
                    <br/>
                    Bootstrap exclusively uses CSS3 for its animations, but Internet
                    Explorer 8 &amp; 9 don't support the
                    necessary CSS properties. Thus,
                    there are no slide transition animations
                    when using these browsers.
                    We
                    have intentionally decided not to include jQuery-based fallbacks
                    for
                    the transitions.
                </b:Paragraph>
